Parameter.LongDescription:
l.291: Cleared at the start of main.c (before the main while loop) after setting DC_Relay_OFF
l.631: Set if command is received with {"bat": "1"}
l.635: Cleared if command is received with {"bat": "0"}

l.732: Cleared if the previous loop had isCamData == 1 and the current loop has isCamData == 0
l.869: Set if(isCamData == 1) AND if(sent_camera_packet_cnt==0)
l.902 and l.905: Cleared if(sent_camera_packet_cnt>=960). Note: at the same time as Camera_ToCPU_End() and isCamData=0;

CustomAlgorithm.AlgorithmText:
s = Status.rawValue;

if (s < 20) {
	Status_BAT.rawValue = 0;
	Status_WCUT.rawValue = 0;
} else if (s < 70) {
	Status_BAT.rawValue = 1;
	Status_WCUT.rawValue = 0;
	s = s - 20;
} else {
	Status_BAT.rawValue = 1;
	Status_WCUT.rawValue = 1;
	s = s - 70;
}

Status_TLM.rawValue = s & 1;
Status_CAM.rawValue = (s >> 1) & 1;
Status_MOVE.rawValue = (s >> 2) & 1;
Status_NORX.rawValue = (s >> 3) & 1;
Status_ICUT.rawValue = (s >> 4) & 1;
